      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready for your dream ride? I\u2019m parting with my absolute beauty of a car, and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged and meticulously cared for. Not a single flaw to be found inside or out. It drives like an absolute dream and looks even better in person. You really have to see this one to believe it\u2014come take it for a spin!",
