    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered icon. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six exhibits perfect compression and instantaneous throttle response via its six individual throttle bodies. Mechanically overhauled with a reinforced rear subframe and comprehensive double-VANOS bulletproofing, this chassis retains its original factory kinematics. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission engages with mechanical precision, routing power to a flawless M-Variable limited-slip differential. Every bushing, seal, and heat shield is in showroom condition, free of thermal cycling fatigue or fluid seepage. A true turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
